[00:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'All right. So, Pomelli, if you haven\'t seen it, is a free AI marketing tool from Google Labs. It launched back in October 2025 and Google has been shipping updates aggressively. October, they launched Business DNA, which scans'

[00:13] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'your website and learns your brand. Then January this year, they added Animate, which turns static images into videos using Wayo 3.1. And now they added photo shoot which uses nanobanana to turn a'

[00:28] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'single product photo into studio quality shots. Now I\'ll be honest AI product photography isn\'t really new. There are paid tools that really do a good job. But what makes Pomellle interesting is'

[00:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'the full pipeline. You\'re not just getting a pretty picture. You\'re also getting brand extraction, product photography, campaign creation, and video all in one single and mind you'

[00:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'free tool. So, let me walk you through the whole thing. Today, I\'m going to start from scratch, take a product, run it through Pomelli end to end, and show you what a small business owner or someone who is in the marketing team can'

[01:07] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'actually get done in less than 10 minutes. Quick disclaimer, all opinions are my own and do [music] not belong to my employer. All right, with that, let\'s get into it. So today, I\'m going to take you through five different use cases'

[01:19] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'that you can do using Pomelli. And for that, I\'m going to select a real business, which is Brooklyn candlestudio.com. So here are the five use cases we\'re going to look at in the next few minutes. Number one, how do you really create studio quality product'

[01:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'photos from a single image, keeping all the brand aesthetics, brand tone, and all of those things in mind. Number two, generating lifestyle content for Instagram. Again, keeping the brand aesthetics and everything in mind.'

[01:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Number three, building a full seasonal marketing campaign. Number four would be turning those assets into video for reals and Tik Tok. And number five will be exploring new creative concepts with different types of AI prompts all from'

[01:57] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'one tool which is going to be Google Pom. So in order for you to access Google Pom, you\'ll have to come to labs.google.com and then you will be greeted with this particular landing page. So here you'

[02:10] [scene:talk]
